snippet.title: Galaxy on Fire™ on Zeebo - official Trailer
snippet.description: From the Java mobile to the iPhone and now the Zeebo: the multi-award-winning outer space adventure Galaxy on Fire™ will be available for the Zeebo system in Brazil in October 2009.
